                            <span class="score-value">{demoData.main.confidence}pt</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="explanation-step">
                    <span class="step-number">2</span>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>最適戦略を自動選択</h3>
                        <p>スコアに応じて、少点数型・バランス型・高配当型から最適な戦略を自動判定します。</p>
                        <div class="strategy-selected">
                            <span class="strategy-icon">✅</span>
                            <span class="strategy-name">{actualStrategy}</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="strategy-reason">{actualDescription}</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="explanation-step">
                    <span class="step-number">3</span>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>買い目を自動絞り込み</h3>
                        <p>選択された戦略の買い目を、累積スコア順にソートして上位のみを抽出します。</p>
                        <div class="bet-count">
                            <span class="count-icon">🎯</span>
                            <span class="count-value">{demoData.betCount}点</span>
                            <span class="count-label">に絞り込み</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 出走馬分析 -->
        <div class="horses-analysis">
            <h2>🐎 出走馬分析</h2>

            <!-- 本命 -->
            <div class="horse-card main">
                <div class="horse-header">
                    <span class="horse-mark">◎</span>
                    <span class="horse-number">{demoData.main.number}</span>
                    <h3 class="horse-name">{demoData.main.name}</h3>
                    <span class="horse-role">{demoData.main.role}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="horse-details">
                    <div class="horse-rating">
                        <span class="rating-label">総合評価:</span>
                        <span class="rating-stars">{demoData.main.rating}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="horse-score">
